      },
      "date": "2024-09-12 19:54:36.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+1\n\nI was thinking to just make a copy from current linux list.h (which presumably already matches the code style) rather than updating the style of an old copy?\n\nIf that is too much, or it drags in extra complexity that we don't want, then I'm OK to just fix the style.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
